responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "81F098E74AE912507AB8B696F6CD4F0D", "Precious reminders of life! They are worth a deal to me, but not while I am dead as you see. I\'m sure any merchant will make an offer for them. Not half as much as they\'re worth though, in my humble opinion.")
